jQuery plugin useful for adding a “human touch” to data. 

Examples:

apnumber
1 becomes one
2 becomes two

intcomma
1337 becomes 1,337
1000000 becomes 1,000,000

intword
1000000 becomes 1.0 million
1000000000 becomes 1.0 billion

naturalday
April 16, 2012 becomes today
April 15, 2012 becomes yesterday

ordinal
1 becomes 1st
2 becomes 2nd

...